Ingredients Sauce: 1 tbsp Soy Sauce 2 tbsp Sugar 3 tbsp Gochujang 1 tsp Garlic (diced) 1 tbsp red chilli flakes or &ldquo;Gochugaru&rdquo;
Stock: Anchovy broth (optional) 3 cups Water Enoki mushrooms Green onion Cabbage 500g Rice Cakes Eggs Ramen noodles
Recipe Mix the sauce together Bring water to boil Add anchovy and simmer Mix in the sauces Throw in the veggies and rice cakes and stir till sauce thickens Add the boiled eggs and ramen Wait for a few mins till the ramen is cooked and then serve!! Optional - sprinkle seasame seeds on top!
